<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nuevo Pago Registrado</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #2d3748;
      background-color: #edf2f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a365d;
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 40px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0 / 100% 100% 0 0;
    }
    .header-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 15px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 35px 35px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a365d;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .detail-section {
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .detail-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 14px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .detail-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .detail-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background-color: #ebf4ff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .detail-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #718096;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .detail-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #2d3748;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .money-section {
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .money-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;
    }
    .money-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .money-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a5568;
    }
    .money-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2d3748;
    }
    .money-value.positive {
      color: #059669;
    }
    .money-value.negative {
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    .amount-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c5282 0%, #1a365d 100%);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-top: 25px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .amount-label {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .amount-value {
      color: white;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .notes-card {
      background-color: #fffbeb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-top: 25px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .notes-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .notes-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .notes-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #92400e;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .notes-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #78350f;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      padding: 25px 35px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #a0aec0;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer p + p {
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Nuevo Pago Registrado</h1>
      <p>Notificaci√≥n del Sistema</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Se ha registrado un nuevo pago en el sistema:</p>
      
      <div class="detail-section">
        <div class="section-title">üìã Informaci√≥n del Pago</div>
        
        <div class="detail-item">
          <div class="detail-icon">üë©</div>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <div class="detail-label">Empleada</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{employeeName}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-item">
          <div class="detail-icon">üìÖ</div>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <div class="detail-label">Fecha de Pago</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{paymentDate}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-item">
          <div class="detail-icon">üè¢</div>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <div class="detail-label">Empleador</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{employerName}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="money-section">
        <div class="section-title">üíµ Detalles del Monto</div>
        
        <div class="money-row">
          <span class="money-label">Salario Base</span>
          <span class="money-value">{{baseSalary}}</span>
        </div>
        
        {{#if bonuses}}
        <div class="money-row">
          <span class="money-label">Bonificaciones</span>
          <span class="money-value positive">{{bonuses}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        {{#if deductions}}
        <div class="money-row">
          <span class="money-label">Deducciones</span>
          <span class="money-value negative">{{deductions}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      
      <div class="amount-card">
        <div class="amount-label">Total Pagado</div>
        <div class="amount-value">${{totalAmount}}</div>
      </div>
      
      {{#if notes}}
      <div class="notes-card">
        <div class="notes-icon">üìù</div>
        <div class="notes-content">
          <div class="notes-title">Notas</div>
          <div class="notes-text">{{notes}}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Mensaje autom√°tico del Sistema de Gesti√≥n de Pagos</p>
      <p>Por favor no responder a este correo</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>